# Design System — Visual Language

## COLORS

Two modes, same token names. Never use raw hex values in code — always reference tokens.

### Dark Mode
```
background.base      #0D1B2A
background.layer     #1A2A3A
background.float     #243447
surface              #2E4057

accent.warm          #F4A261
accent.hot           #E76F51
accent.cool          #2A9D8F

text.primary         #F0EAD6
text.secondary       #A8B2C0
text.muted           #5C6E82

border               #1E3248
star                 #F4A261
```

### Light Mode
```
background.base      #FAF7F2
background.layer     #F0EBE1
background.float     #FFFFFF
surface              #EDE4D8

accent.warm          #2D6A4F
accent.hot           #1B4332
accent.cool          #2A9D8F

text.primary         #1A1A1A
text.secondary       #5C5C5C
text.muted           #9E9E9E

border               #DDD5C8
star                 #E8A838
```

